Converse Pro Leather Lola Bunny Space Jam (PS)
results.story: Made for little kids, the Converse Pro Leather PS ‘Lola’ singles out one of LeBron James’ Tune Squad teammates from ‘Space Jam: A New Legacy.’ In addition to ‘Lola Bunny’ imprinted on the heel tab, the character’s golden tan fur is referenced on the sneaker’s Star Chevron branding. The white leather upper is further embellished with mismatched graphics embroidered on the lateral heel of each shoe: Lola herself graces the right shoe, while her raised finger holds aloft a basketball on the left. A durable rubber cupsole anchors the low-profile silhouette.

Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Hi Made With Love (GS)
results.story: Dropping as part of the brand’s Valentine’s Day collection, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘White’ carries a traditional canvas upper festooned with unique details in honor of February 14. They include heart-printed laces, an embroidered heart on the lateral side and a ‘Made With Love’ graphic on the opposite side. Underfoot, the white rubber outsole features a traditional diamond traction pattern and an all-over print made up of additional red hearts.

Converse Chuck Taylor All-Star Hi Scooby-Doo Good Guys Bad Guys (GS)
results.story: Made for big kids, the Scooby-Doo x Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘The Gang and Villains’ is drawn from a larger collection celebrating the long-running animated franchise. The white canvas upper features a graphic print on the lateral side that depicts Scooby and Shaggy in a frightened emotional state. A black woven tongue tag is inscribed with ‘Scooby-Doo!’ on the exterior side and ‘Ruh-Roh!’ on the interior.

results.name: Converse UNT1TL3D Hi Not a Chuck White (GS)
results.story: The Converse UNT1TL3D High GS distorts and exaggerates iconic All Star elements. Arrived in July 2019, this kid's iteration has an 'Egret' canvas upper featuring an allover 'Not A Chuck' print with text embroidery, Star Chevron insignia and a streamlined patch on the outer ankle. Bright lining and an overlapped heel logo further the bold styling. A midsole with 3D stripes and color-pop outsole rubber wrap the up sneaker's look.

results.name: Converse UNT1TL3D Hi Not A Chuck Black (GS)
results.story: Launched in July 2019, the Converse UNT1TL3D High GS twists and magnifies the silhouette's iconic distinctions. This kid's edition in black canvas is covered in an allover 'Not A Chuck' graphic with embroidered text, a Star Chevron logo and an All-Star cutout patch. The bold aesthetic continues with color-pop lining and overlapped heel branding. 3D stripes across the midsole and a bright rubber outsole pull it all together.

results.name: Converse One Star Ox Hello Kitty Black (GS)
results.story: Converse released a colorway in collaboration with Hello Kitty that celebrates both the Japanese cartoon character and the iconic One Star silhouette. The Hello Kitty x One Star Suede Low Top GS 'Black' features a black suede upper with pink and white Hello Kitty graphics on the heel, sides and tongue. The lining features a polka dot print, and the classic Hello Kitty bow sits above the One Star.

Converse One Star Ox Hello Kitty Pink (GS)
results.story: Converse partnered with Hello Kitty to release a grade school exclusive that celebrates both the Japanese cartoon character and the iconic One Star. The Hello Kitty x One Star Suede Low Top GS 'Prism Pink' features a soft suede Prism Pink upper with Hello Kitty graphics on the heel, side and tongue, a polka-dot-printed lining and contrasting white detailing. The classic Hello Kitty bow rests above the One Star.
